xrr - C Extension for Python and pyxrr - wrapper
************************************************

Author:  Carsten Richter
Contact: carsten.richter@ikz-berlin.de
Website: http://carichte.github.io/pyxrr/



Requirements:
    - C compiler (openMP for parallel processing)
    - python3
    - python-dev
    - Python Packages:
            - numpy
            - lmfit
            - appdirs
            - matplotlib
            - scipy
            - h5py
            - pandas
            (- PyQt5 if one wants to use the GUI)


